Dialogue: 1,0:22:20.94,0:22:26.54,Yuri004-ED-JP-land-2,,0,0,10,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}寄り添う　二人の物語
Dialogue: 1,0:22:26.54,0:22:32.11,Yuri004-ED-JP-land-2,,0,0,10,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}色を付け道になり　交ざり合う
