Dialogue: 1,0:22:37.98,0:22:41.82,Yuri004-ED-JP-land-2,,0,0,10,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}抱え込んだ昨日さえ
Dialogue: 1,0:22:41.82,0:22:43.60,Yuri004-ED-JP-land-2,,0,0,10,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}愛してゆこう
Dialogue: 1,0:22:43.60,0:22:46.62,Yuri004-ED-JP-land-2,,0,0,10,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}重なる　メロディーが
Dialogue: 1,0:22:46.62,0:22:48.86,Yuri004-ED-JP-land-2,,0,0,10,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}明日も　ずっと
Dialogue: 1,0:22:48.86,0:22:51.58,Yuri004-ED-JP-land-2,,0,0,10,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}続きますように
Dialogue: 1,0:22:51.58,0:22:57.80,Yuri004-ED-JP-land-2,,0,0,10,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}願い込めた空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.68,0:23:01.60,Yuri004-ED-JP-side-2,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}君の声が
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.60,0:23:04.52,Yuri004-ED-JP-side-2,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}聞こえるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.52,0:23:07.39,Yuri004-ED-JP-side-2,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}この歌声
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.39,0:23:10.15,Yuri004-ED-JP-side-2,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}響かせよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.15,0:23:12.32,Yuri004-ED-JP-side-2,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}どんな時でも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.32,0:23:14.53,Yuri004-ED-JP-side-2,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}二人で　乘り越えてゆ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.53,0:23:19.30,Yuri004-ED-JP-side-2,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}こう譲れない絆を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.30,0:23:26.41,Yuri004-ED-JP-side-2,,0,1820,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}かけがえのない　君だから
Dialogue: 1,0:23:27.79,0:23:32.21,Yuri004-ED-JP-land-2,,0,0,10,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}Only for you
