Dialogue: 2,0:22:26.54,0:22:32.11,Yuri004-ED-CHS-land-2,,0,0,60,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}行路色彩艳丽　交织一起
Dialogue: 2,0:22:32.11,0:22:35.82,Yuri004-ED-CHS-land-2,,0,0,60,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}是我心满意足　还是不足
Dialogue: 2,0:22:35.82,0:22:37.98,Yuri004-ED-CHS-land-2,,0,0,60,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}旧事循环往复　如此而已
Dialogue: 2,0:22:37.98,0:22:41.82,Yuri004-ED-CHS-land-2,,0,0,60,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}相拥于怀　不过昨日记忆
Dialogue: 2,0:22:41.82,0:22:43.60,Yuri004-ED-CHS-land-2,,0,0,60,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}让我们一起　坠入爱河里
Dialogue: 2,0:22:43.60,0:22:46.62,Yuri004-ED-CHS-land-2,,0,0,60,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}重波叠浪　音律乐章
Dialogue: 2,0:22:46.62,0:22:48.86,Yuri004-ED-CHS-land-2,,0,0,60,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}明天也要　直到永远
Dialogue: 2,0:22:48.86,0:22:51.58,Yuri004-ED-CHS-land-2,,0,0,60,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}但愿海枯石烂
Dialogue: 2,0:22:51.58,0:22:57.80,Yuri004-ED-CHS-land-2,,0,0,60,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}也要实现飞天的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.68,0:23:01.60,Yuri004-ED-CHS-side-2,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}你的心声啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.60,0:23:04.52,Yuri004-ED-CHS-side-2,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}我能听到呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.52,0:23:07.39,Yuri004-ED-CHS-side-2,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}这首旋律啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.39,0:23:10.15,Yuri004-ED-CHS-side-2,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}于我心中回响
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.15,0:23:12.32,Yuri004-ED-CHS-side-2,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}无论何时啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.32,0:23:14.53,Yuri004-ED-CHS-side-2,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}两人一起　乘风破浪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.53,0:23:19.30,Yuri004-ED-CHS-side-2,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}这份坚不可摧的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.30,0:23:26.41,Yuri004-ED-CHS-side-2,,1830,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}独一无二不可替代　是因为你呀
Dialogue: 2,0:23:27.79,0:23:32.21,Yuri004-ED-CHS-land-2,,0,0,60,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4}只为你一人呀
